<p><div align="center"><table width="50%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr>
<td width="150"><br></td>
<td align="center"><b>
<i>Lasioglossum mesillense</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">&#40;Cockerell, 1898&#41;</font></b><br>
<small><i>Halictus nymphalis race </i>mesillensis Cockerell, 1898; <i>Dialictus mesillensis </i>&#40;Cockerell, 1898&#41;; <i>Halictus &#40;Chloralictus&#41; clarissimus </i>Ellis, 1914; <i>Dialictus clarissimus </i>&#40;Ellis, 1914&#41;; <i>Halictus &#40;Chloralictus&#41; perexiguus </i>Sandhouse, 1924; <i>Dialictus perexiguus </i>&#40;Sandhouse, 1924&#41;</small><p>
<a href="/mp/20q?search=Life">Life</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Insecta">Insecta</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Hymenoptera">Hymenoptera</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Apoidea">Apoidea</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Halictidae">Halictidae</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Lasioglossum">Lasioglossum</a>
<br><small>Subgenus: <a href="/mp/20p?see=Dialictus&name=Lasioglossum&flags=subgenus:"><i>Dialictus</i></a></small>
</td></tr></table><p>
<p>
<table width="80%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tr><td>
<div align="center">
